flowchart TB
  I["Stable interpreter<br/>what the browser loads"]
  P["Encrypted bytecode<br/>program"]
  VM["Virtual machine<br/>runs the bytecode"]
  SNAP["Encrypted snapshot<br/>sent for attestation"]
  AT["Self verification"]
  DOM["Environment and DOM checks"]
  I --> P
  P --> VM
  VM --> SNAP
  VM -.guards.-> AT
  VM -.inspects.-> DOM
